=== 请求转发

添加本地域名解析
[source, bash]
----
cat <<EOF >> /etc/hosts
127.0.0.1 test.testdemo.com
EOF
----

[source, bash]
----
vim /etc/nginx/nginx.conf

#添加一个server模块测试
server {
        listen      80;
        server_name test.testdemo.com;

        # 转发请求到 http://www.example.com
        location / {
            proxy_pass http://www.baidu.com;
        }
    }
----

重载nginx
[source, bash]
----
nginx -t && nginx -s reload
----

浏览器访问 [http://test.testdemo.com]

页面将自动跳转到百度首页
